replies.body:
1:   Halycon1, Hold Fast and Fantasy (one with elves and orcs, everyone hated it, but it reminds me of Lord Of The Rings. )

2: I have recently got into Ghost Recon Wildlands.

3: I really enjoy doing small details (eg. Patterns) as you probably saw from Heaven on your build server. I have recently discovered terraforming and im really getting into that, you can see that from my other un-named map on your server.

4: I find your a really really nice guy, who is easy to talk too. I love your voice, i don't know where your from though xD I feel your a very good map dev as i see you have a clear passion for all the avicus maps. Could do with some help to touch up some of my maps though :D

replies.body:
You are really nice! You probably don't remember this but you are the main reason I carried on playing Avicus. At one point I nearly quit as I was so bad at PvP that everyone always killed me, I just slowly got tired of losing. Anyways it was on Rendezvous Ctw and I was about to leave but then I accidently 10 hearted you.... You just had diamond rank back then. You asked me what mouse I had and what texture pack I used. You were the first person who actually talked to me. Back when my ign was Rocky_1969 (cringe) Every time after I looked for you in the lobbies, you must of had a break or possibly time zones but I never could find you. Anyways since then I started talking more and I slowly tuned into what I am today. So overall I'm not sure whether or not to thank you or not. You probably don't remember but thanks anyways! 

I was really surprised as I felt like I did terrible in the interview. Of course I was really happy I had to stop my self from mic spamming and then just look dumb when I said "thanks he he" xD

My trial is going well so far I've been met with a lot of circumstances that I hadn't really thought of before.
